                          rdfs:comment """This category of VRDMaterialWorldThing refers to either 1) things that don't sit comfortably within one of the other 3 categories (Natural, Engineered or Cultural things), or 2) classes used in property domain/range restrictions that contain mixtures of things that span the othe 3 categories (Natural, Engineered or Cultural) of things.

