                rdfs:domain vrd:VRDWorldThing ;
                rdfs:range vrd:Image ;
                rdfs:comment "A property to associate a VRD material world thing (an individual object) with the VRD image from whose visual relationship annotations the thing originated." .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/nesy4vrd/ontologies/vrd_world#standBehind
vrd:standBehind rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
                rdfs:subPropertyOf vrd:behind ;
