###  http://www.semanticweb.org/nesy4vrd/ontologies/vrd_world#hasCoordinateXmax
vrd:hasCoordinateXmax rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty ,
                               owl:FunctionalProperty ;
                      rdfs:domain vrd:Bbox ;
                      rdfs:range xsd:integer ;
                      rdfs:comment "The 'xmax' integer coordinate of a bounding box specification." .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/nesy4vrd/ontologies/vrd_world#hasCoordinateXmin
vrd:hasCoordinateXmin rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty ,
